Sentencas: High-performing electrolytes at low operating temperatures have become an inevitable trend in the development of low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells (LT-SOFCs).
Titulo: High-performing and stable semiconductor yttrium-doped gadolinium electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Such electrolytes have drawn significant attention due to their appeal for high performance.
Titulo: High-performing and stable semiconductor yttrium-doped gadolinium electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Herein, we propose a new material by doping Y3+ into Gd2O3 for LT-SOFC electrolyte use.
Titulo: High-performing and stable semiconductor yttrium-doped gadolinium electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The prepared material was characterized in terms of crystal structure, surface, and interface properties, followed by its application in LT-SOFCs.
Titulo: High-performing and stable semiconductor yttrium-doped gadolinium electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: YDG delivered promising SOFC performance with a power density of 1046 mW cm(-2) at 550 degrees C along with high ionic conductivity of 0.19 S cm(-1).
Titulo: High-performing and stable semiconductor yttrium-doped gadolinium electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, impedance spectra revealed that YDG exhibited the least ohmic resistance of 0.06-0.09 omega cm(2) at 550-460 degrees
Titulo: High-performing and stable semiconductor yttrium-doped gadolinium electrolyte for low-temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: C. Furthermore, stable operation for 60 h demonstrated the chemical stability of the material in reduced temperature environments.
